flowRoot.flowPara: Selecting a list item displays the keyboard layout.
When there is more than one input source, close buttons are displayed, and it is possible to reorder by dragging.
Input source order in the list sets the default switching order.
If the window isn't focused when a language download is complete, a notification is shown.

Restart required infobar; this is shown if a different display language has been selected but isn't yet in effect. It shouldn't be shown at the same time as the downloading language infobar.
Missing resource infobar - shown if a language is being used but the relevant flatpak extensions haven't been installed.
